; lingbot-learned-visual-real-life.fk — non-test learned visual door.
;
; Returns compact live evidence after Form computes four complete authentic
; DINOv2-L/14 patch-projection tokens over four real-life video frames.
; preludes: form/form-stdlib/core.fk form/form-stdlib/str-byte-at.fk form/form-stdlib/form-fs.fk form/form-stdlib/file-byte-window.fk form/form-stdlib/crc32.fk model/lingbot-pytorch-checkpoint.fk form/form-stdlib/transformer-numerics.fk cognition/transformer-block.fk model/lingbot-vision-input.fk model/lingbot-learned-patch.fk model/lingbot-learned-real-life.fk

